- netdata: add authentication to the dashboard (port 19999)
- promtail + loki to redirect systemd-journald and syslog logs to be viewed in
  kibana: https://github.com/grafana/loki/tree/master/docs/clients/promtail
- Colocar a configuração abaixo no playbook do docker:
```
{
  "bip" : "1.1.1.0/16",
  "mtu": 1500,
  "log-driver": "journald"
}
```

